<item>
            <title>[LU-11137] Enable ZFS  compression on MDT by default</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-11137</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;We should enable data compression on ZFS MDT filesystems by default in &lt;tt&gt;mkfs.lustre&lt;/tt&gt; for new MDTs.  There is already ZFS compression for metadata enabled at all times, but with DoM we will also store data on the MDT.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Since the MDT will typically also be located on flash storage, from a cost and performance perspective it makes sense to compress the data that is stored there.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="52680">LU-11137</key>
            <summary>Enable ZFS  compression on MDT by default</summary>
