                                                                            <comments>
                            <comment id="322878" author="adilger" created="Sun, 16 Jan 2022 09:07:23 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;This is probably something that should be decided by the admin. Unlike ldiskfs, it is possible to change ZFS configuration after installation, so enabling compression can be done at any time. &lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="322870" author="tappro" created="Sun, 16 Jan 2022 08:20:35 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Andreas, is this still worth to implement or outdated?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="230202" author="adilger" created="Wed, 11 Jul 2018 23:58:18 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;It would be good to verify that this does not affect performance on the MDT significantly.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
